00:29:15,800 --> 00:29:17,160
He never came down again.

585
00:29:19,280 --> 00:29:20,520
Between her and me,

586
00:29:21,080 --> 00:29:22,560
there’s always this barrier.

587
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:24,760
It can’t be crossed.

588
00:29:27,560 --> 00:29:29,240
After Rui Yu married Nan Chenxiao,

589
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:30,720
it seemed to help civil and military harmony.

590
00:29:30,760 --> 00:29:32,320
It seems to have had some effect.

591
00:29:33,840 --> 00:29:34,760
Maybe.

592
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:37,000
Anyway, I think no civil official is good.

593
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:39,560
Your Majesty

594
00:29:39,720 --> 00:29:40,760
must be just like his father,

595
00:29:40,760 --> 00:29:42,160
full of scheming thoughts.

596
00:29:42,240 --> 00:29:43,720
Always fearing generals will seize power.

597
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:47,760
What if he thinks differently than you?

598
00:29:47,760 --> 00:29:49,240
What if he wants to improve civil-military ties?

599
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:52,920
If he truly wants to improve those relations,

600
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:54,680
my father wouldn’t have been jailed for nothing.

601
00:29:59,720 --> 00:30:00,760
Let’s not talk about this.

602
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:01,520
Let’s go.

603
00:30:01,720 --> 00:30:02,920
I’ll take you ahead for a walk.

604
00:30:03,240 --> 00:30:04,760
Let me show you some uncommon herbs.

605
00:30:11,440 --> 00:30:11,920
Let’s go.

606
00:30:17,000 --> 00:30:18,200
This foxtail grass,

607
00:30:18,200 --> 00:30:19,760
removes heat, dampness, and reduces swelling.

608
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:21,000
Shepherd’s purse is edible

609
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:22,480
and treats red, painful eyes.

610
00:30:22,760 --> 00:30:23,800
As for Cang’er,

611
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:25,480
every part of it can be used as medicine.

612
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:27,320
Its root cures erysipelas.

613
00:30:27,520 --> 00:30:29,080
It also treats dysentery.

614
00:30:29,080 --> 00:30:30,240
Its stem and leaves

615
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,600
can treat dizziness and vertigo.

616
00:30:32,560 --> 00:30:33,760
And its fruit

617
00:30:33,760 --> 00:30:35,280
can treat nasal congestion and runny nose.

618
00:30:35,320 --> 00:30:37,600
Also relieves pain from wind-cold and dampness.

619
00:30:37,840 --> 00:30:39,800
You could say the whole plant is a remedy.
